replies.body:
Yeah, schools aren't the best way of seeing how smart someone is because teacher might take it easy and/or the difficulty of the school might differ from place to place. Before I moved, I was getting all A's with an occasional B+. Now since I moved, I've gotten 2 A's and 18 A+'s. 
Anyways, it doesn't depend if you're getting A+'s or not on this test because it has no idea about your grades. If you're getting C's, you can still get a 100% on this test, although it's not probable. But yeah, I think this test is pretty inaccurate xD
